metadata.name: STAPLEGUTTER Series One Holder Bundle
metadata.description: Birds of a feather run the streets together. The Gutter Cat Gang teamed up with New York based streetwear pioneer Jeff Staple to announce an official GUTTER CAT GANG x STAPLE PIGEON collaboration - STAPLEGUTTER Series One. This STAPLEGUTTER Series One Holder Bundle has been forged into a digital collectible and redeemed to receive physical STAPLEGUTTER Series One merchandise; including a long sleeve tee in ecru, canvas tote bag, and holder exclusive bucket hat.
